{
  "stem": "7069.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was little embarrassed in front of the other people, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so-- and he turned to me after a while and said, you know something?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I want you know, young fellow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know very well what's the matter with me, in very sharp, nice, educated type tone.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I'm wondering, he says, I don't know what's the matter with you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm wondering about you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He says, no, but I don't need to answer any of your questions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I want to know something, just so you can be satisfied.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- this is my oldest suit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is the way I'm going to come to work, whether you like it or not.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, you see some people say that-- well, let me put it this way very first.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of my colleagues there had noticed that little encounter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he came to me and he says, hey, don't you know who this man is?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, no, and what does is matter?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, of course it matters, but I was too stupid to see it at that time, at that moment.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He says, this man is the chief surgeon of the largest hospital in Berlin, the Charite, which still exists-- was in East Berlin as long as it was East Berlin.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And besides, he was the, the, the chief of teaching surgery at the university.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was this man with his fine hands, with fine fingers, and his personality and the studies that were made to save lives and to operate on people, he was forced, because he was a Jew, to dig ditches, ditches in the ground, and ruin, of course, his hands, possibly.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, was never, never dug around in his own backyard, I guess, and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
